    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition" subtype="transcription">
                <p>
                    <persName>Publius Oppius</persName>filius
                    <lb/>Camilia [.3 char. .]
                    <lb/>CIO <placeName>Ravenna</placeName>
                    <lb/>miles <rs type="miliary">legionis V
                    <lb/><num value="5">5</num>    Macedonicae</rs>, optio,
                    <lb/>vixit annos
                    <lb/>XXX, militavit annos VIIII.
                    <lb/>Hic situs est.
                    <lb/>Heres fecit.
                </p>
            </div>
          <div type="translation">
                <p>
                    <persName>P(ublius) Oppi[us</persName>, son of...],
 	         <lb/>of (the tribe of) Camilia,
	         <lb/>...cio, of <placeName>Ravenna</placeName>,
	         <lb/>soldier of the<rs type="miliary">Legio V
                    <lb/><num value="5">5</num>	Macedonica</rs>, (of the rank of) optio,
	         <lb/>lived
	         <lb/>30 years, served in the army nine years
 	         <lb/>(and) is buried here.
	         <lb/>(His) heir made (this tombstone). 
                </p>
            </div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>This funerary inscription is documented from the Week 3 assignment list. Not much information can be found for this artifact online.</p>
            </div>
